Method Detail

compareTo

public int compareTo(Enlargement<E> other)
Compares this Enlargement with the specified Enlargement. First the increasement of the overlap will be compared. If both are equal the increasement of the volume will be compared. If also both are equal the volumes of both nodes will be compared. If both are equal the ids of the nodes will be compared.

Specified by:
